&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technical Expertise&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;UX Design: You define UX quality standards, push teams toward innovation, and drive best practices across research, strategy, and execution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Visual Design: You champion high-quality visual execution and stay current on trends, emerging technologies, and tooling.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Product Strategy: You ensure design work aligns with overarching product roadmaps, release strategies, and market positioning.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Critique &amp;amp; Collaboration: You guide teams in fostering a culture of constructive critique, both internally and with clients.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Research: You leverage qualitative and quantitative data to inform and validate design decisions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Content Design: You advocate for clear, compelling communication that aligns with brand strategy and user experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Leadership &amp;amp; Influence&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
